title: 90ML
subTitle: A man with fetal alcohol syndrome keeps himself alive by drinking a certain amount of alcohol. However, things change when he falls in love with a beautiful woman.

title: Vedaa
subTitle: Vedaa, a victim of caste discrimination, trains as a boxer under Abhimanyu and strives to seek justice for the murder of her siblings.

title: Police Police
subTitle: Ranadheer and Ravikanth, two policemen, turn foes after Ravikanth gets involved in antisocial activities. Ranadheer then plans to prove Ravikanth is the culprit.

title: Gorilla Gang
subTitle: Four friends join hands to rob a bank with a chimpanzee as their accomplice. However, things do not go the way they have planned.

title: The Faith Show
subTitle: Romildo Ribeiro Soares, a Brazilian televangelist, stresses the importance of faith in the Almighty and explains inner life and how to condition it for the world.

title: Maaligai
subTitle: A female police officer goes to an ancient palace to investigate. However, once she enters the palace, she gets a vision of her past life where she was a fierce and beautiful princess.

title: Vijay The Master
subTitle: Troubled alcoholic teacher JD goes to work at a juvenile reform school. When he realises a dangerous criminal is using students to cover up his crimes, JD sets out to stop him.

title: Andaaz
subTitle: After his sweetheart Kajal marries another man, Raj moves to Cape Town. He eventually agrees to marry Jiya but is shocked to find that she is Kajal's widowed sister-in-law.

title: Surya: The Soldier
subTitle: An orphan raised by his deceased mother's friend, dreams of joining the army. Later, he must leave the love of his life behind when he receives his appointment letter.

title: Simmba
subTitle: Inspector Simmba is a corrupt officer who works for a major smuggler. He finds his values challenged as the gangster's brothers assault his sworn sister.

title: Extra Ordinary Man
subTitle: Abhinay, a struggling artist, meets the woman of his dreams and changes his aim. However, stumbling upon the chance to star in a movie, Abhinay's life takes a drastic turn.

title: Akhanda
subTitle: When the nefarious Varadarajulu plans to attack Murali Krishna, an ardent devotee of Lord Shiva, Akhanda leaves no stone unturned to defeat the evil.

title: Akhanda

title: Khuda Haafiz: 2 - Agni Pariksha
subTitle: After the death of his friend's brother, Sameer and Nargis adopt his daughter Nandini. However, trouble ensues when she gets kidnapped.

title: Aag Ka Gola
subTitle: After losing his mother, an innocent boy raised to become a criminal by a mobster. He later faces threat from his boss when he tries to mend his ways.

title: Yudhra
subTitle: A vengeful youth infiltrates a dangerous cartel to avenge the death of his parents. As he delves deeper, he uncovers shocking truths about his past that challenge his resolve and moral boundaries.

title: The Faith Show
subTitle: Romildo Ribeiro Soares, a Brazilian televangelist, stresses the importance of faith in the Almighty and explains inner life and how to condition it for the world.

title: Dhartiputra
subTitle: Yashpal tries to rape Jeeva and her husband, Shiva, stops him while she manages to escape. However, Yashpal kills him and she vows to avenge his death.

title: Singh Is Bling
subTitle: When a carefree Raftar Singh is given the choice of getting married or going to Goa for a business deal, he chooses the latter. Little does he know of the adventure he is about to embark on.

title: Jaanwar
subTitle: A criminal changes the course of his life when he decides to raise a baby who has survived a train crash, but chaos ensues when his past begins to haunt him.

title: Dhamaal
subTitle: Four lazy friends learn about a hidden treasure in Goa and set out to find it. However, a police inspector learns about their plan and begins to pursue them.

title: Maya Puthagum
subTitle: Guru, an assistant director, dreams of a dragon, which leads him to a mysterious book and its owner. The latter instructs him to meet a producer at a palace to film the manuscript's contents.

title: Pushpa 2: The Rule
subTitle: A powerful smuggler goes head-to-head with a vengeful enemy while controlling politics and managing high-stakes confrontations. A public apology sparks a tense showdown, culminating in a challenge.

title: Uri: The Surgical Strike
subTitle: Major Vihaan Singh Shergill of the Indian Army leads a covert operation against a group of militants who attacked a base in Uri, Kashmir, in 2016 and killed many soldiers.

title: Uri: The Surgical Strike
subTitle: Major Vihaan Singh Shergill of the Indian Army leads a covert operation against a group of militants who attacked a base in Uri, Kashmir, in 2016 and killed many soldiers.

title: Pataas
subTitle: After moving to the city, Kalyan befriends GK, a notorious villain. Later, Kalyan regrets his actions when his friend ruthlessly murders an orphaned girl.

title: Runway 34
subTitle: Upon dealing with the rough climate in Cochin, two pilots make a risky landing in Thiruvananthapuram. But trouble ensues when personnel from the AAIB probes the matter.

title: Ek Joshila
subTitle: Vamsi is hell-bent on seeking revenge and rescue his lover Krishnaveni, from the clutches of an evil landlord, Basavanna, who murdered his best friend.

title: Entertainment
subTitle: Akhil, an underdog and a failure, comes to know that his real father is a rich diamond merchant who has just passed away. When he goes to retrieve his wealth, he learns that a dog has inherited it.

title: Hum Saath Saath Hain
subTitle: Ramkishan and Mamta lead a happy life with their three sons. But when their daughter faces a tragedy, Mamta gets instigated by her close friends, and she embitters her heart towards her stepson Vivek.

title: Crew
subTitle: Three ambitious female cabin attendants from Mumbai get caught in a web of lies during their pursuit of dreams, leading to an unexpected heist.

title: Singham Again
subTitle: Drawing parallels to the Ramayana, Bajirao Singham and his team embark on a mission to rescue his wife, confronting a mysterious and formidable antagonist along the way.

title: Vettaiyan
subTitle: The rape and murder of a teacher leads Athiyan, a policeman known for encounter killing, to unknowingly murder an innocent man. Soon, a guilty Athiyan sets out to reinvestigate her case.

title: Antim: The Final Truth
subTitle: Rahul runs away from his poverty-stricken village life to become a gangster in the city. There, he locks horns with an upstanding policeman who tries to set him on the right path.
